lass="RedColor"&gt;Level 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sword of Valiance (AoC) - &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Level 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;*&lt;/b&gt;Zelda's Sacred Bow is on par with Link's Sacred Bow (Zelda's uses Light arrows instead) so for balance purposes I made it require Link's level 3 in order to obtain it (technically speaking Zelda's bows would be level 4, 5 and 6)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;**&lt;/b&gt;Fi's Level 1 sword: The Goddess Sword is &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;not included&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; in this mod since it is already in the game. It can be obtained via &lt;b&gt;Amiibo&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;***&lt;/b&gt;Young Link's Level 1 sword: The Fierce Deity Sword is &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;not included&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; in this mod since it is already in the game. It can be obtained via &lt;b&gt;Amiibo&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;****&lt;/b&gt;Toon Link's Level 1 is the Hero's Sword and Shield. The Hero's Shield is &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;not included&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in this mod since it is already in the game. It can be obtained via &lt;b&gt;Amiibo&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Final Words:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I had a lot of fun putting this mod together. The mod is not perfect yet as I still have some gripes with how some of the weapons turned out. I'm still new to the modding scene and there's a lot I'm not familiar with so maybe after I learn more tricks and such I'll revisit this mod and update it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I expect there to be bugs, glitches and typos, so if there are any issues present with the mod, please let me know and I'll try to fix them as best as I can.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Enjoy!</description>
